'''Macarthur Fortune Holding LLC''' is a US-based global asset management firm founded by a group of  investment professionals. The company has worked together with management teams and entrepreneurs in the video game, cloud computing, artificial intelligence robotics industries to create long-term sustainable growth. Macarthur Fortune’s investments span the full range of opportunities including venture capital, private equity, merger and acquisition and public companies.{{CiteGeneral|url=https://www.jagex.com/en-GB/news/4yL8qH/macarthur-fortune-holding-llc-acquires-jagex- |title=MacArthur Fortune Holding LLC Acquires Jagex|accessdate=2020-06-06 |author=Jagex |name=pressrelease}}

It was announced on April 28th 2020 that Macarthur Fortune Holding's private managed fund, Platinum Fortune LP, had acquired a 100% stake in Jagex for $530 million USD from [[Fukong Interactive Entertainment]].{{CiteGeneral|url=https://secure.runescape.com/m=news/company-announcement |title=Company Announcement |accessdate=2020-06-06 |author=Jagex}} Platinum Fortune LP has a focus on the global video game market, and targets global video game companies and designs strategies to help them grow user base and revenue.{{NamedRef|pressrelease}}

